heir own learning trajectory by generating and solving progressively more challenging problems, requiring only a formal verifier rather than human guidance.\n\n**Limitations and Constraints:**\nSemi-autonomous validation is expected to mature with formal checks and high-throughput labs, with local recursive self-improvement cells in narrow toolchains, still bounded by goals, governance, and physics."],"durationSeconds":8.199545415999367,"searchCount":1},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"f0c82626-620a-4775-9994-d1f01a388ccc","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
