{"parentUuid":"c8a0db67-bcb6-4bad-a0c4-69461479e250","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"ae50cd09b1428afac","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01Mzvu5nArvKXyuusiy4maiZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018BK4C4iiiwENBYFpCiqXwX","name":"WebFetch","input":{"url":"https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/XHd75cuHhWcBDd8to/recursive-self-improvement-is-three-different-things","prompt":"Extract exact verbatim quotes arguing that self-improvement is bounded by the base model, that scaffolding/orchestration improvements are bounded by the underlying model's capabilities, and any claims about verifiers/evaluators being a precondition. Give exact wording with quotation marks."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":323,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2447,"cache_read_input_tokens":18581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2447,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcG2C19cyhTQ1oQG2PwGP","attributionAgent":"general-purpose","attributionSkill":"deep-research","type":"assistant","uuid":"fff8b713-82a3-4340-a9b4-a84215fe1ae7","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:36:38.017Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
{"parentUuid":"fff8b713-82a3-4340-a9b4-a84215fe1ae7","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"ae50cd09b1428afac","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01Mzvu5nArvKXyuusiy4maiZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01E6Z6iDXVcqRoExr5zB68yq","name":"WebFetch","input":{"url":"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/darwin-godel-machine","prompt":"Extract exact verbatim quotes about (1) the Darwin Godel Machine's reliance on a strong benchmark/verifier (SWE-bench, Polyglot) for its empirical fitness, (2) its capabilities being bounded by the frozen foundation/base model, and (3) any critical analysis that gains depend on the evaluator and base model rather than true self-improvement. Give exact wording with quotation marks."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":323,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2447,"cache_read_input_tokens":18581,"output_tokens":458,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2447},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":323,"output_tokens":458,"cache_read_input_tokens":18581,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2447,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2447,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcG2C19cyhTQ1oQG2PwGP","attributionAgent":"general-purpose","attributionSkill":"deep-research","type":"assistant","uuid":"000d26b4-5ee1-426a-84f0-a4f82d225cc8","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:36:40.178Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
{"parentUuid":"000d26b4-5ee1-426a-84f0-a4f82d225cc8","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"96f7ce82-27af-4c04-ae02-270c4873a922","agentId":"ae50cd09b1428afac","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01E6Z6iDXVcqRoExr5zB68yq","type":"tool_result","content":"# Key Quotes from the Darwin Gödel Machine Article\n\n## (1) Reliance on Benchmarks for Empirical Fitness\n\n\"The DGM's capacity for self-improvement was rigorously evaluated on two coding benchmarks: SWE-bench (a subset of verified tasks) and Polyglot (tasks in multiple programming languages).\"\n\n\"the entire process relies on the assumption that the chosen benchmarks are faithful proxies for the desired complex abilities.\"\n\n## (2) Bounded by Frozen Foundation Model\n\n\"The use of frozen FMs enables the system to concentrate on innovating the design and workflows of the coding agents, rather than undertaking the computationally intensive task of retraining the FMs themselves.\"\n\n\"the system's current reliance on frozen FMs means its ultimate capabilities are bounded by these models, and it doesn't yet learn to improve the FMs themselves.\"\n\n## (3) Critical Analysis of True Self-Improvement Claims\n\n\"One key direction is to expand the DGM's self-modification capabilities beyond its current Python codebase to include rewriting its own training scripts, enabling it to update the underlying FMs themselves.\"\n\nThis admission indicates current limitations prevent genuine recursive self-improvement beyond the base model's constraints."}]},"uuid":"73cb5401-b391-46e6-826c-b0143d9552b9","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:36:46.104Z","toolUseResult":{"bytes":264301,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Key Quotes from the Darwin Gödel Machine Article\n\n## (1) Reliance on Benchmarks for Empirical Fitness\n\n\"The DGM's capacity for self-improvement was rigorously evaluated on two coding benchmarks: SWE-bench (a subset of verified tasks) and Polyglot (tasks in multiple programming languages).\"\n\n\"the entire process relies on the assumption that the chosen benchmarks are faithful proxies for the desired complex abilities.\"\n\n## (2) Bounded by Frozen Foundation Model\n\n\"The use of frozen FMs enables the system to concentrate on innovating the design and workflows of the coding agents, rather than undertaking the computationally intensive task of retraining the FMs themselves.\"\n\n\"the system's current reliance on frozen FMs means its ultimate capabilities are bounded by these models, and it doesn't yet learn to improve the FMs themselves.\"\n\n## (3) Critical Analysis of True Self-Improvement Claims\n\n\"One key direction is to expand the DGM's self-modification capabilities beyond its current Python codebase to include rewriting its own training scripts, enabling it to update the underlying FMs themselves.\"\n\nThis admission indicates current limitations prevent genuine recursive self-improvement beyond the base model's constraints.","durationMs":5697,"url":"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/darwin-godel-machine"},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"000d26b4-5ee1-426a-84f0-a4f82d225cc8","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
